# Guessing Game - Python Project

## Description
Computer chooses a number 1-10, user guesses until correct. Gives hints.

## Learning Notes Matched
- Loops: `while` for repeated guesses  
- Conditionals: feedback based on comparison  
- Input validation: ensure numeric, in range  
- Functions: modular code  

## Example Gameplay

Your guess (1-10): 3
Too low!
Your guess (1-10): 7
Too high!
Your guess (1-10): 5
Correct! You guessed in 3 attempts.


## How to Run
```bash
python guessing_game.py
